item.title: CVE-2018-9866|2024-08-05T07:24:56.291Z -- sonicwall -- global%20management%20system%20%28gms%29
item.description: A vulnerability in lack of validation of user-supplied parameters pass to XML-RPC calls on SonicWall Global Management System (GMS) virtual appliance's, allow remote user to execute arbitrary code. This vulnerability affected GMS version 8.1 and earlier.
